What is this?
-------------

Camera Wire is a software to connect your camera to your computer to
perform operation like image retrieval and thethered shooting.

Albeit tied to Niepce Digital by design, it can operate independently.

It is currently work in progress.

To build is you need the following:
-----------------------------------

A C++ compiler
gtk+ 2.8
cairo 1.1
gtkmm 2.12
giomm
gconf 2.x
cairomm
libxml > 2.5.0
boost 1.34
 -boost test (for the unit test)
exempi >= 2.0.0
libopenraw >= 0.0.5
geglmm >= 0.0.22
gegl >= 0.0.22
babl

Camera Wire is being developed on Linux. It should build and work on
other UNIX systems.




